# Intel 8052 RTL Model

The 8052 is an 8-bit microcontroller originally developed by Intel in 1980.
I've recently resurrected an old project that I started during my time as a
PhD student in 1999. Back then, I needed some synthesizable models, and the
8052 seemed like a suitable candidate.

I'm now creating a new repository for this project and plan to make minor
improvements to the original model, as time permits.

## Packages

$ brew update
$ brew upgrade
$ brew install nvc
$ brew install sdcc
$ brew install emacs

## Testing

; replace cast.hex with any of the other test programs

$ cd test/
$ make
$ cd ../utils
$ make
$ ./mkrom ../test/cast.hex
$ mv i8051_rom.vhd ../src
$ cd ../src
$ ./sim
